{"type": "article", "id": 22984, "title": "新德里品牌 Paul Matter 新品", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-29T07:08:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115128FVA6U9JmT3dQ7pfB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是印度新德里一家新成立的灯具品牌  Paul Matter 在推出的一组产品，包括两个灯具和一个蜡烛台。产品都使用了黄铜材料体现出传统和复古的色彩，特征在于灯具的悬挂杆的下面是可调整的，使灯具的朝向有了倾斜的角度，搭配相互交错的挂杆，立刻让这组灯有了艺术气息，也能表达出使用者的个性。<a href=\"http://www.paulmatter.com/\">这里是该品牌的主页。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115127z6ogLPkBFXr2QNZl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151273hrjECmxe0GFKd27.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151271ZWn5w4SbkMCLzBV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115128uhE02LSd1sY4azoZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}